\cf0 One of the goblins here is responsible for the paintings and the group are rather proud of him and his work. If the characters immediately compliment them on the work they may react in a friendly manner. Otherwise they\'92ll loose their arrows at the lead character in unison and cry out for support from 49 who will arrive in 2 rounds.\
