\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\i \cf0 The chamber appears to be a guard room, with tables, bunks and sword racks. Several goblins are here reaching for their weapons, and it seems you have disturbed an unpleasant game of chance involving dice, hammers and live mice. 
