\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\i\b0 \cf0 Goblins stand around resting on spears watching another group seeming to be playing some sort of game that involves dice and crude wooden miniatures. A great deal of shouting, pointing and dice rolling is going on, all orchestrated by a larger goblin that seems to have the biggest pile of wooden figures. A crude playing board is chalked out on the table they sit around. 
