\b 60. Guards of the King\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\i\b0 \cf0 Serious looking armoured goblins with big axes scramble to defensive positions when you enter this large chamber,  and suddenly ear splitting shrieks sound out, coming from what appear to be huge purple mushrooms that are attached to a rotting log. \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\i0 \cf0 The Shriekers have been especially grown to ignore goblins by the Fungal King. The goblins here are the loyal guards of the King and will brook no intruders. With the shriekers sending out the alarm goblins will start arriving after 4 rounds in random waves for 2d4 rounds. \
\
