\i \cf0 This hidden door leads to a small chamber which appears to have had some sort of fire or explosion in it judging by the scorch marks obscuring the walls. A blackened skeleton lies next to an open chest that seems to have retained it\'92s content and contains gold, jewellery and what looks like a potion bottle.
